        <mxCell id="wsdc" value="&lt;b&gt;WS2025-DC1&lt;/b&gt;  ·  172.22.0.10&#10;&#10;Windows Server 2025 Standard Eval&#10;Server Core · FFL = WinThreshold (2016)&#10;&#10;&lt;i&gt;lab.test&lt;/i&gt; forest root&#10;&#10;MSFT WS2025-2602 Security Baseline&#10;linked to OU=Domain Controllers&#10;(LDAP sign + channel binding, SMB sign,&#10;Kerberos AES, Defender, VBS, Domain Security)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;align=center;spacingTop=8" vertex="1" parent="1">
